### ================================================================
### TrakCare Data Sync — Pull episodes from central
### Server: http://demo01.tcdb.vtas.cl.intersystems.com
### Endpoint: GET /demo01/tcoffline/getData
### Auth: HTTP Basic (demo / demodemo)
###
### The local backend calls this endpoint during downstream sync.
### Use these requests to inspect what the central server returns
### directly, without going through the local backend.
### ================================================================

@tcBaseUrl = http://demo01.tcdb.vtas.cl.intersystems.com
@tcDataEndpoint = /demo01/tcoffline/getData

# Basic ZGVtbzpkZW1vZGVtbw== = base64("demo:demodemo")
@tcAuth = Basic ZGVtbzpkZW1vZGVtbw==

### Pull all episodes (no filter)
GET {{tcBaseUrl}}{{tcDataEndpoint}}
Authorization: {{tcAuth}}

### Pull episodes for a specific user filter
GET {{tcBaseUrl}}{{tcDataEndpoint}}?user=doctest
Authorization: {{tcAuth}}

### Pull episodes with department filter
GET {{tcBaseUrl}}{{tcDataEndpoint}}?user=doctest&dept=EMERGENCIA
Authorization: {{tcAuth}}

### Pull with the default demo filter from .env.example
GET {{tcBaseUrl}}{{tcDataEndpoint}}?user=demo
Authorization: {{tcAuth}}

### ================================================================
### Validate sync round-trip via local backend
### Login → pull from central → verify local episodes updated
### ================================================================

@localUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Step 1 — Login to local backend
# @name localLogin
POST {{localUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Step 2 — Check current sync stats before pull
GET {{localUrl}}/sync/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{localLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### Step 3 — Trigger downstream sync (pull from central)
POST {{localUrl}}/sync/from-central
Authorization: Bearer {{localLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### Step 4 — Check sync stats after pull (last_sync should be updated)
GET {{localUrl}}/sync/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{localLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### Step 5 — List episodes to confirm data arrived
GET {{localUrl}}/episodes?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{localLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### Step 6 — Check central connectivity status
GET {{localUrl}}/health/central
Authorization: Bearer {{localLogin.response.body.access_token}}
